title: The League Season 4 Premier Audio Book Party (Steve Rannazzisi)
itunes:title: The League Season 4 Premier Audio Book Party with Steve Rannazzisi
description: Steve Rannazzisi and I were on our way down to San Diego to perform at the La Jolla Comedy Store for the weekend and we thought we'd record a short podcast on our way to promote the new season of The League on FX and just to have fun. It's pretty funny and devoid of any specific subjects. Just two idiot comics shooting the shit for half an hour.
